have to be a fight?

691
00:51:04,000 --> 00:51:05,750
- I don't know.
- Why?

692
00:51:06,209 --> 00:51:08,959
You said the PET scan report
was normal.

693
00:51:09,125 --> 00:51:12,042
I meant the cancer
was in control for the time being.

694
00:51:12,167 --> 00:51:15,750
