Okay?

761
00:57:36,375 --> 00:57:37,375
Okay.

762
00:57:37,958 --> 00:57:40,500
All the reports by 5 o'clock, please.

763
00:57:40,583 --> 00:57:41,875
Okay. Sure, sir.

764
00:57:45,417 --> 00:57:46,417
Dad...

765
00:57:47,750 --> 00:57:48,750
Manny?

766
00:57:48,958 --> 00:57:50,500
